  "title": "IT System Analyst (Healthcare)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company’s Profile:</strong></p><p>Our client is a leading public healthcare institution, recognised for its excellence in healthcare, research, and education. The organisation has been ranked among The Straits Times’ Best Employers and listed in the Top 10 of Singapore’s Leading Employer Awards, reflecting its strong commitment to employee growth and engagement.</p><p>With a people-first culture, they are dedicated to staff development and workplace well-being. You can look forward to a meaningful career with an organisation that values innovation, compassion, and excellence in advancing health for the community.</p><p>Work Location: Kent Ridge</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead Informatics initiatives e.g. Predictive Modelling and data structure optimisation. </li><li>Review and make recommendations to optimise Laboratory Information System functions and contribute to decision making. </li><li>Monitor and support Laboratory Information System applications. </li><li>Manage Project Change Requests (PCRs) and Operational Service Requests (OSRs), including review, deconflict and testing. </li><li>Assist to ensure laboratory accreditation compliance in systems. </li><li>Assist in conducting system administration and compliance for the department. </li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 – 3 years System Analyst experience, in healthcare environments will be a strong advantage</li><li>Possess Degree in IT or equivalent</li></ul><p><br />Interested candidates may <strong>whatsapp your resume to 8977 7062</strong>. Only shortlisted applicants will be contacted.</p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to the collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by company relating to this job application.</p><p>Cassie Chan | R2197426</p><p>EnviroDynamics Solutions Pte Ltd | EA No: 12C6285</p>",
